like specifically like

00:00:33.001 --> 00:00:34.040
super creative

00:00:34.041 --> 00:00:35.360
like aesthetic

00:00:35.361 --> 00:00:39.160
beautiful content that obviously takes a lot of her time and editing and

00:00:39.161 --> 00:00:42.940
and energy and I told her that it's just hard

00:00:43.240 --> 00:00:44.880
I think so often

00:00:44.881 --> 00:00:48.720
we try to pretend that everything is gonna be sunshine and rainbows and like

00:00:48.721 --> 00:00:50.000
we've got this mama

