when someone struggling

00:00:53.921 --> 00:00:55.120
all they wanna know is that like

00:00:55.121 --> 00:00:56.280
it's okay that they're struggling

00:00:56.281 --> 00:00:57.760
so I basically just told her

00:00:57.761 --> 00:00:59.320
I was like it is this hard

00:00:59.321 --> 00:01:00.760
it's super fucking hard

00:01:00.761 --> 00:01:02.660
this is the chapter of hard

00:01:02.840 --> 00:01:04.680
um but it's a temporary chapter

