and it does get easier

00:01:05.761 --> 00:01:06.760
and you'll get through it

00:01:06.761 --> 00:01:10.240
and if you need to take a step back from things that are draining your energy

00:01:10.241 --> 00:01:11.920
or resources or time

00:01:11.921 --> 00:01:15.120
think that's okay because you're now in a different chapter

00:01:15.121 --> 00:01:16.480
it doesn't mean you're always gonna be here

00:01:16.481 --> 00:01:20.040
but I think the best advice you can give to a new mom who either has one kid

00:01:20.041 --> 00:01:23.440
or two kids or is going through that transition and is having a tough time is

00:01:23.441 --> 00:01:25.840
you're having a tough time because it is tough

00:01:25.841 --> 00:01:26.760
and the more you can like

00:01:26.761 --> 00:01:31.400
settle into the knowledge that it is hard and you're gonna struggle and

00:01:31.401 --> 00:01:33.260
and it it's okay

00:01:33.400 --> 00:01:36.400
it's it's okay to be having a hard time when

00:01:36.401 --> 00:01:37.540
when something's hard

00:01:37.560 --> 00:01:38.200
you have to like

00:01:38.201 --> 00:01:40.340
surrender to the chapter that you're in

00:01:40.440 --> 00:01:42.500
and look to your friends who have been through it

00:01:42.520 --> 00:01:45.780
because we're testaments to the fact that you're gonna make it through it too
